  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-6 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Eleven factors are assessed with achievedLevel meeting or exceeding requiredLevel; two factors (Numerical solver error and Use error) are marked not-applicable with thorough rationale. Decision: Accepted.",
