      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "rationale": "Equivalency between validation experiment input parameters and COU deployment conditions is confirmed: pump geometry is identical (same CAD file); operating points span the COU envelope; blood analogue fluid is matched to physiological haematocrit (40 ± 3 %); temperature controlled to 37 ± 0.5 °C. Deviations are documented and shown to be within the Monte Carlo uncertainty bounds.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
