        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "A parameter-by-parameter equivalency table must demonstrate that validation experiment inputs are representative of COU deployment conditions. Any deviations must be quantified and shown to fall within the uncertainty bounds used in the Monte Carlo analysis. Gradation 3 requires formal equivalency documentation signed by the responsible engineer."
      }
